title: La Maison en Petits Cubes (The House of Small Cubes)
description:
"As his town is flooded by water, an old man is forced to add additional levels onto his home with bricks (cubes) in order to stay dry. But when he accidentally drops his favorite smoking pipe into the lower levels of his home, his search for the pipe eventually makes him relive scenes from his eventful life."--IMDB 

2008 Academy Award winner for short animated films.

This is an upload of a video I downloaded. The mkv video was not supported by my Samsung tv's media player even though it supports mkv files. To fix the error in the file I ran it through AVC Ultimate, retaining the original settings, but changing the aspect ratio to 16:9. The original did not fill the screen horizontally or vertically. The conversion retains the original size, 704x480, so there should be no noticeable distortion
